      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"hope\" stuff... it's just what people say to feel better about themselves. It doesn't change the fact that it's the same cycle every single time. No matter the strategy, the outcome is always the same. It's like I'm trapped in a machine that's designed to break me. It feels less like a \"struggle\" and more like a fundamental flaw in how I'm built. The loop is the only thing that's real anymore.",
